.premium/one-killed-11-wounded-in-shooting-attack-at-west-bank-checkpoint/0000018d-d026-da8e-abbd-dff612750000</guid></item><item><title>以色列欧洲歌唱大赛歌曲《十月雨》可能因过于政治化而被取消参赛资格</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-eurovision-song-october-rain-could-be-disqualified-for-being-too-political/0000018d-d096-d234-abdf-fadf3d800000</link><description>这首歌提到了在战争中死去的士兵，欧洲广播联盟正在审查这首歌，该联盟将就其资格做出决定。过去，歌曲曾因政治原因被取消参赛资格，包括 Georgia 2009 年的参赛歌曲“I Don&amp;#39;t Want to Put In”</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 12:23:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-eurovision-song-october-rain-could-be-disqualified-for-being-too-political/0000018d-d096-d234-abdf-fadf3d800000</guid></item><item><title>美国联合航空将于三月恢复飞往以色列的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/united-airlines-set-to-resume-flights-to-israel-in-march/0000018d-d05e-d06c-abbd-d8fe1eb70000</link><description>这家总部位于美国的航空公司将于 3 月 6 日恢复纽瓦克和特拉维夫之间的每日航班 ■ 在此之前，美联航预计将运营该航线并在德国中转</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 10:46:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/united-airlines-set-to-resume-flights-to-israel-in-march/0000018d-d05e-d06c-abbd-d8fe1eb70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列因在 Facebook 上发布有关 10 月 7 日袭击事件的“支持恐怖分子”而扣押巴勒斯坦裔美国妇女</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-holding-palestinian-american-woman-for-pro-terror-posts-about-october-7-attacks/0000018d-ce4b-da8e-abbd-cfff0b8b0000</link><description>一名军事法庭法官下令美国出生的巴勒斯坦人萨马赫·埃斯梅尔保释，他说：“我非常怀疑居住在美国的美国公民在 Facebook 上发帖在以色列是否会被视为犯罪”</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 10:08:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-holding-palestinian-american-woman-for-pro-terror-posts-about-october-7-attacks/0000018d-ce4b-da8e-abbd-cfff0b8b0000</guid></i