-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-rejects-petition-to-nullify-ben-gvirs-appointment/0000018d-cd12-deb3-afdd-ffb289cc0000</link><description>高等法院裁定，没有理由干预内塔尼亚胡总理选择伊塔马尔·本-格维尔担任以色列国家安全部长</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 19:35:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-rejects-petition-to-nullify-ben-gvirs-appointment/0000018d-cd12-deb3-afdd-ffb289cc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列航空公司将向以色列国防军士兵赠送数千张免费机票，但附带一些注意事项</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/el-al-to-gift-thousands-of-free-plane-tickets-to-idf-soldiers-with-some-caveats/0000018d-cc97-d914-a5ad-ce97b9bc0000</link><description>该网站推出后一小时内所有可用门票都被抢购一空，数万名以色列士兵空手而归</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 17:25:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/el-al-to-gift-thousands-of-free-plane-tickets-to-idf-soldiers-with-some-caveats/0000018d-cc97-d914-a5ad-ce97b9bc0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列人拒绝内塔尼亚胡。这并不意味着他们接受左翼观点”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-02-21/ty-article-podcast/israelis-are-rejecting-netanyahu-that-doesnt-mean-they-are-embracing-left-wing-views/0000018d-cc31-d914-a5ad-ce333c600000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 16:39:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-02-21/ty-article-podcast/israelis-are-rejecting-netanyahu-that-doesnt-mean-they-are-embracing-left-wing-views/0000018d-cc31-d914-a5ad-ce333c600000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 138 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-138/0000018d-cc74-deb3-afdd-fff45f360000</link><description>以色列国防军高级律师表示，以色列国防军发现其在加沙的行为超出了犯罪门槛。 美国表示，国际法院不能在不考虑以色列安全需求的情况下命令以色列立即从巴勒斯坦领土撤军。加沙北部 ■ 据报道，40 岁妇女和 5 岁女孩在以色列国防军对黎巴嫩南部的袭击中丧生 ■ 战争结束 138 天后，您需要了解以下信息</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 16:35:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-138/0000018d-cc74-deb3-afdd-fff45f360000</guid></item><item><title>以色列机场管理局表示，美联航和达美航空将恢复飞往特拉维夫的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/united-delta-to-resume-flights-to-tel-aviv-israels-airport-authority-says/0000018d-cc5e-d914-a5ad-ce5ec3b90000</link><description>虽然航空公司尚未正式宣布恢复飞往以色列的航班，但美联航网站已从 3 月起提供飞往以色列的机票 ■ 美国航空公司将于 10 月初停止飞往以色列的航班</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 16:19:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/united-delta-to-resume-flights-to-tel-aviv-israels-airport-authority-says/0000018d-cc5e-d914-a5ad-ce5ec3b90000</guid></item><item><title>最新民意调查显示，大多数以色列人表示加沙不太可能取得“绝对胜利”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/most-israelis-say-absolute-victory-in-gaza-unlikely-according-to-new-poll/0000018d-cc0e-d6e9-a38d-fc1fe3ab0000</link><description>“绝对胜利”这个词是故意选择的，因为它已成为本杰明·内塔尼亚胡总理在新闻发布会和外语采访中喜欢用的词，尽管他不愿定义其实际含义</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 15:48:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/most-israelis-say-absolute-victory-in-gaza-unlikely-according-to-new-poll/0000018d-cc0e-d6e9-a38d-fc1fe3ab0000</guid></item><item><title>哈佛亲巴勒斯坦教职人员团体为分享带有反犹太主义图像的帖子而道歉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/harvard-pro-palestinian-faculty-group-apologizes-for-sharing-post-with-antisemitic-image/0000018d-cc0e-d6e9-a38d-fc1f836d0000</link><description>哈佛大学谴责了这张照片，并表示其管理委员会将从现在开始审查这些帖子。该大学写道：“我们以最强烈的措辞谴责这些帖子”</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 15:31:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/harvard-pro-palestinian-faculty-group-apologizes-for-sharing-post-with-antisemitic-image/0000018d-cc0e-d6e9-a38d-fc1f836d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国称联合国最高法院不应敦促以色列立即从巴勒斯坦声称拥有主权的土地上撤军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/un-top-court-shouldnt-urge-israel-to-immediately-withdraw-from-palestinian-claimed-lands/0000018d-cbd1-dd47-adfd-dbf528560000</link><description>在国际法院就以色列占领领土举行听证会的第三天，美国代表告诉专家组不要试图“通过针对仅关注某一方行为的问题的咨询意见”来解决以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 15:05:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/un-top-court-shouldnt-urge-israel-to-immediately-withdraw-from-palestinian-claimed-lands/0000018d-cbd1-dd47-adfd-dbf528560000</guid></item></channel></rss>